 combine a character string and properties.</span> </p><p class="rvps3"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="imgspec/Oper-Propriete141.png"></p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts30"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts7">You can use the codification <span class="rvts7"><span class="rvts18">&quot;{13}&quot;</span></span></span> <span class="rvts7">to insert a line break.</span> </p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts7"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps3"> <span class="rvts30"><br></span> </p><p></p></div><div id="topic_footer"><div id="topic_footer_content"> Copyright Â© 2017 by Visiativ. All Rights Reserved. </div></div>